1. determine which sensor the player is at
if player outside
2. close inside door
3. depressurize airlock
4. open outside door
5. wait for player to reach middle sensor
6. close outside door
7. pressurize airlock
8. open inside door
9. wait for player to reach inside sensor
10. close inside door

if player inside
2. close outside door
3. pressurize airlock
4. open inside door
5. wait for player to reach middle sensor
6. close inside door
7. depressurize airlock
8. open outside door
9. wait for player to reach inside sensor
10. close outside door